{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f5845cd6d0","title":"对中共中央、国务院关于除四害讲卫生指示稿的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dec105da6f","index":0,"year":1958,"month":2,"day":7,"articleId":"f5845cd6d0"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"75387adef2","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡养木，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、毛泽东的秘书。即本篇二。文中用宋体字排印的是毛泽东加写的文字。即本篇三。文中用宋体字排印的是毛泽东加写的文字。"}],"contents":[{"id":"746b9ba9c3","type":"title","text":"对中共中央、国务院关于除四害讲卫生指示稿的批语和修改","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"},{"id":"75387adef2","type":"paragraph","text":"即退胡乔木同志。在第六页作了一点修改，现在许多基层单位就是这样做的。在第七页上加了灭臭虫跳备一句“","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"},{"id":"e13cb0d8e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"},{"id":"9270659cfd","type":"paragraph","text":"二月七日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"},{"id":"0a52bd7be3","type":"paragraph","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"},{"id":"b2c8e61643","type":"paragraph","text":"各基层单位（例如一个生产队，一个工段，一条街道）的除四害讲卫生工作应该每星期检查一次，各较大单位（例如一个合作","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"},{"id":"d8d49c8b9b","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]中共中央、国务院1958年2月12日《关于除四害讲卫生的指示》在1958年2月13日《人民日报》上发表。社，一个乡，城市一个工厂，一个区）应该每月检查评比一次，年终应该大检查总评比一次，以便为实现长期计划打下基础。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"},{"id":"2b5e55390f","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"},{"id":"704afda352","type":"paragraph","text":"向群众提出的具体口号各地可以因地制宜，例如除四害在有血吸虫病的地区要加上消灭钉螺，有黑热病地区要加上消灭白岭子，有臭虫、跳备的地区要加上消灭臭虫、跳蚤，讲卫生在城市中可以包括劝止随地吐疫，在工厂中可以着重防治职业病等等。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0"}],"page":{"id":"2dd96ddf77","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"f5845cd6d0","start":520,"end":521}}}},"__N_SSG":true}